info.name: Spotify Web API
info.description:
This Postman Collection contains a set of automated tests designed to verify the functionality of the Spotify Web API.

It focuses on CRUD operations related to playlists, including creating plalists, adding and removing tracks and reordering them.

The collection is divided into positive and negative test suites to ensure both valid and invalid behaviors are properly validated.

Main goals:

- Verify correct API responses for valid requests (functional testing).
    
- Ensure appropriate error handling and response messages for invalid inputs.
    
- Validate response codes, structure, messages according to Spotify API documentation.
